 </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="fr">
            <p> a) <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <supplied reason="lost">Untel fils de Bai</supplied>eias, <supplied reason="lost">Untel fils de Khar</supplied>matiôn, <supplied reason="lost">un tel fils de</supplied> Damasanôr, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost">p</supplied>olis
